Investment Managers
We manage investment portfolios for a wide range of clients, including  pension plans, foundations, endowments, and individuals.Our firm is independently owned and managed by a team of investment professionals. 



Investment Philosophy

We believe that long-term stock price appreciation is based on long-term earnings growth.
Learn More »


Equity Strategies

We invest in multinational companies, whose products and services aim to capture the majority of growing profit pools around the globe. 
Learn More »


Fixed Income

Our objective is to provide a positive return annually, thereby preserving the capital base even during declining markets.
