Christopher B. Sarofim is Vice Chairman of Fayez Sarofim & Co., President of Sarofim International Management Company and a Director of The Sarofim Group.  He is a member of Fayez Sarofim & Co.’s Executive, Investment and Finance Committees, a co-manager of the mutual funds that Fayez Sarofim & Co. manages for The Dreyfus Corporation and a portfolio manager for a variety of institutional and high net worth clients.  Mr. Sarofim joined the Firm in 1988 as an Associate.
